*desklet-goodweather-0.1 (19 Nov 2003)

  19 Nov 2003; Mike Gardiner <obz@gentoo.org> desklet-goodweather-0.1.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  First version in portage. Uses weather codes available from weather.com (as
  shown in the configure dialog) to give the forecast for the next 5 days

